Game Notes: Shoppy Mart: Steam Edition is the full grocery store cashier experience that many have dreamed about, but few asked for.


Shoppy Mart puts you in the shoes of a grocery store cashier, where it is your job to scan items and stuff them in grocery bags. You'll be required to hand out flyers, mention promotions, and remind people they forgot their reusable bags in the car, all while dealing with rude customers!
